  abstract = {We present a constrained formulation of Dedner et al.'s 
hyperbolic/parabolic divergence cleaning scheme for enforcing the
{$\nabla\cdot$}B=0 constraint in smoothed particle magnetohydrodynamics
(SPMHD) simulations. The constraint we impose is that energy removed
